Gusts 60 to 75 mph expected for the north face of Casper Mountain and higher elevations. * WHERE...Green Mountains and Rattlesnake Range, Natrona County
entry.cap:areaDesc: Casper Mountain; Green Mountains and Rattlesnake Range; Natrona County Lower Elevations
